cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper deals with provenance metadata, which is commonly used in databases (cs.DB) and security (cs.CR) settings. The paper also discusses the use of policies to control access to sensitive information, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper presents a tool for interactive experimentation, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
